# Claude local settings (do not publish)
.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# Coursework artifacts: kept locally as a personal record but not part of
# the public release. Includes assignment.pdf, the CS-137 final-report
# tex/submission/figures/slides, the Tufts evaluator wrappers, and the
# Tufts HPC SLURM batch files. Internal notes (progress.md, audit logs)
# also live here.
CS137-assignment/

# docs/ holds only the public-facing arXiv paper PDF; everything else is
# private working drafts kept locally.
docs/*
!docs/paper.pdf

# report/ — paper source is private from v1.6 onward; we ship only the
# built docs/paper.pdf publicly. A local symlink at `report/arxiv` -> the
# private working area (`本地文件/report/arxiv/`) lets the scripts keep
# their familiar paths without leaking the private location into public
# code. Both the symlink and any contents under report/ are gitignored.
reports

# Recovery-only scratch files (session-specific)
本地文件